==Latin==
===Suffix===
'''-ulus''', '''[[-ula]]''', '''[[-ulum]]'''

The form '''-ulus''' is the masculine singular [[nominative]] [[case]].

# suffix added to various words to produce a [[diminutive]] form indicating small or little

====Example====


{| border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"
|----- bgcolor="ccffff"
| Word || Diminutive
|-----
| calx, calc- || [[calculus]]
|-----
| rex, reg- || [[regulus]]
|}

